ActStandards Council of Canada Act
PrecisAppointment of TAYT WINNITOY of Cobble Hill, British Columbia, to be a member of the Standards Council of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, effective February 5, 2019, in the place of Sara Jane Snook, whose term will expire.
